 2009-17192009-10-08,  ,  ,  ,  CAN POST
ActCanada Post Corporation Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Services and Fees Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE SPECIAL SERVICES AND FEES REGULATIONS, will increase the rate charged for registered mail delivered in Canada, effective January 11, 2010. The amendments implement a $0.45 increase, to $7.95, for registered mail delivered in Canada.
